                %br
            .col-sm-4
              .gradient-text
                %h2 Devise
              %h3.font-text
                %p  Devise is a flexible authentication solution for Rails based on Warden. It:
                %br
                * Is Rack based.
                %br
                * Is a complete MVC solution based on Rails engines.
                %br
                * Allows you to have multiple models signed in at the same time.
                %br
                * Is based on a modularity concept: use just what you really need.
                %br 
                * Installation of the gem and adding Authentication to an Application.
